  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for all <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur Flamethrower Units</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damage output</span>, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">burn time</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fuel efficiency</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于所有<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯火焰喷射器单元</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害输出</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃烧时间</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯火焰噴射器元件</span>的所有<span class=\"name name-technology\">重大升級</span>。使用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組靈活度高，但在安裝完成前，確切的升級數據<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害輸出</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃燒時間</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>。"
